21 'บ    This simple program can be used effectively to convert hexadecimal   บ
23 'บ numbers to decimal and decimal to hexadecimal. This is of value when    บ
25 'บ working with some poke-peek values or converting some CHR$(&Hnn) to     บ
27 'บ decimal values, such as when zapping disk sectors.                      บ
29 'บ                                                                         บ
31 'บ    At the prompt, enter the decimal number as "20" w/o quotes and the   บ
33 'บ HEX$ value will be displayed.  Enter a HEX number as "&H234" also w/o   บ
35 'บ quotes and both the decimal and HEX$ will be displayed.                 บ
